{"tid":666661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前懲教員涉姦親女　陪審團有人搭錯𨋢坐錯位而遭解散","createTime":"2018-05-16T05:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T05:56:00.000Z","uid":48083,"like":114,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"0790e7876c59d2a581138484b22850c362301d4f","tid":666661,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:21:34.000Z","msg":"退休6旬懲教人員涉嫌非禮及強姦親生女兒，被控強姦和非禮等共5罪。法官今日(16日)解散6男1女陪審團，指有2名陪審員今日使用公眾升降機，而未有使用專用通道。其中1人途經法庭，直入休息室，而另一人則曾坐在法庭公眾席，當時律師之間有對話。法官指無論該陪審員是否聽到對話，情況亦不理想，為對被告或他人公平，遂決定解散陪審團，法庭稍後會再選陪審團審理案件。 <br />\n<br />\n本身已婚的60歲男被告，被控3項非禮、1項向16歲以下兒童作出猥褻行為和1項強姦罪。控罪指出，被告於2008至09年間，非禮女事主X及向X作出猥褻行為。此外，被告亦被控於2013年某日，在牛頭角彩德邨強姦X。X現年19歲，首度疑遭性侵時年僅9歲。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180516/mobile/bkn-20180516103331867-0516_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180516%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180516103331867-0516_00822_001.html&d=UFwGXX8V4%2F2YAQ8xCHZgtL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=73605f4f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180516/mobile/bkn-20180516103331867-0516_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1fd6bfb9e6aeda60cbaeb2dd415702cca2105947","tid":666661,"uid":145779,"like":173,"dislike":1,"score":172,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:23:54.000Z","msg":"豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a91993e1e7656199407a06400aa77bc9822e60","tid":666661,"uid":144843,"like":251,"dislike":2,"score":249,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:23:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64cc6247685d3643d0fb68cddb25a5f8c158862f","tid":666661,"uid":628,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:24:26.000Z","msg":"岩呀咁撚弱智<br />\n出到黎個結果都ON99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8ef772c8bbf81805ff207943e74c3163a78be3","t